      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i was looking at this new shirt pattern from that one big department store and something feels off about it. it's like this specific kind of small plaid. every time i wear stuff with patterns like this i feel weirdly tired and like i cant focus or speak up for myself. do u think it's possible they design these patterns to actually influence how people act?",
